
--- Windows CLI Basics ---

Where Am I: cd
What's Around Me: dir
Show Hidden Files: dir /a

Moving Around the Filesystem: cd folder_name
Finding the File on the Disk: dir /s task_brief.txt

Navigate to the File: cd <path_to_the task_brief.txt>
Read the File: type task_brief.txt

Who Am I Logged In As: whoami
What Is the Name of This Computer: hostname
What Version of Windows Is This: systeminfo

Network Connectivity: ipconfig
